</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Tag</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Bis zu 3 Tage definieren, an denen das Listing erfolgen soll.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
